OL,4,G2000FCasualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,5,     GThe hospital is in the middle of
OL,6,     Gone of the worst storms in
OL,7,     Gdecades, but that doesn't stop
OL,8,     Gcasualty being busy. It's not
OL,9,     Glong before paramedics bring in
OL,10,     Gthe storm's first victim.
OL,11,G2100FAmbulance: Code Red
OL,12,     GA 64-year-old man collapses at
OL,13,     Gwork with a suspected cardiac
OL,14,     Garrest, and paramedics rush to
OL,15,     Ghelp a woman trapped in her car
OL,16,     Gafter crashing into a fallen tree.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
