OL,4,G2200FA&E After Dark
OL,5,     GA motorcyclist is rushed in for
OL,6,     Gan emergency operation to stop
OL,7,     Ginternal bleeding; a doctor
OL,8,     Gtreats a patient run over by a
OL,9,     Gcar that she herself had just
OL,10,     Gbeen in.
OL,11,G2300FSkin A&E
OL,12,     GThe team's new dermatologist Dr
OL,13,     GMagnus Lynch specialises in
OL,14,     Gfacial surgery and makes an
OL,15,     Gexplosive start with a large
OL,16,     Gjawline cyst. Plus, a man with
OL,17,     Ginfectious warts.
