OL,4,G0200FCasualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,5,     GFour-year-old Skyler is rushed
OL,6,     Ginto Paediatrics care with
OL,7,     Grecurring seizures; 65-year-old
OL,8,     GShaun has tumbled down some
OL,9,     Gsteps; and Eric, 85, has a badly
OL,10,     Gswollen leg.
OL,11,G0245FSkin A&E
OL,12,     GCurtis, 26, has struggled since
OL,13,     Gage ten and faces surgery for a
OL,14,     Gcyst near a nerve.
OL,15,G0335FCar Pound Cops
OL,16,     GFollowing the army of enforcers
OL,17,     Gpatrolling the streets, hunting
OL,18,     Gdown drivers for vehicle
OL,19,     Gviolations, including operations
OL,20,     Gacross from the Isle of Skye and
OL,21,     Gin Surrey.
